data.value: SELECT um_mstr.code_name AS um_name, ac_mstr_sales.ac_code AS ac_code_sales, ac_mstr_sales.ac_name AS ac_name_sales, ac_mstr_disc.ac_code AS ac_code_disc, ac_mstr_disc.ac_name AS ac_name_disc, tax_class.code_name AS sqd_tax_class_name, a.sqd_oid, a.sqd_dom_id, a.sqd_en_id, a.sqd_add_by, a.sqd_add_date, a.sqd_upd_by, a.sqd_upd_date, a.sqd_sq_oid, a.sqd_seq, a.sqd_is_additional_charge, a.sqd_si_id, a.sqd_pt_id, a.sqd_rmks, a.sqd_qty, a.sqd_qty_allocated, a.sqd_qty_picked, a.sqd_qty_shipment, a.sqd_qty_transfer_issue, a.sqd_qty_transfer_receipt, a.sqd_um_conv, a.sqd_qty_real, a.sqd_taxable, a.sqd_tax_inc, a.sqd_tax_class, a.sqd_ppn_type, a.sqd_status, a.sqd_dt, a.sqd_payment, a.sqd_dp, a.sqd_sales_unit, a.sqd_loc_id, a.sqd_serial, a.sqd_pod_oid, c.en_desc, d.si_desc, e.pt_code, e.pt_desc1, e.pt_desc2, e.pt_type, e.pt_ls, sb_mstr_sales.sb_desc, cc_mstr_sales.cc_desc, f.loc_desc, b.sq_code, public.en_mstr.en_desc, b.sq_date, j.tranaprvd_tran_oid, j.tranaprvd_tran_code, j.tranaprvd_name_1, j.tranaprvd_name_2, j.tranaprvd_name_3, j.tranaprvd_name_4, j.tranaprvd_pos_1, j.tranaprvd_pos_2, j.tranaprvd_pos_3, j.tranaprvd_pos_4, j.tranaprvd_name_5, j.tranaprvd_name_6, j.tranaprvd_name_7, j.tranaprvd_name_8, j.tranaprvd_pos_6, j.tranaprvd_pos_5, j.tranaprvd_pos_7, j.tranaprvd_pos_8 FROM public.sqd_det a INNER JOIN sq_mstr b ON (b.sq_oid = a.sqd_sq_oid) INNER JOIN en_mstr c ON (c.en_id = a.sqd_en_id) INNER JOIN si_mstr d ON (d.si_id = a.sqd_si_id) INNER JOIN pt_mstr e ON (e.pt_id = a.sqd_pt_id) INNER JOIN code_mstr um_mstr ON (um_mstr.code_id = a.sqd_um) INNER JOIN ac_mstr ac_mstr_sales ON (ac_mstr_sales.ac_id = a.sqd_sales_ac_id) INNER JOIN sb_mstr sb_mstr_sales ON (sb_mstr_sales.sb_id = a.sqd_sales_sb_id) INNER JOIN cc_mstr cc_mstr_sales ON (cc_mstr_sales.cc_id = a.sqd_sales_cc_id) LEFT OUTER JOIN ac_mstr ac_mstr_disc ON (ac_mstr_disc.ac_id = a.sqd_sales_ac_id) INNER JOIN code_mstr tax_class ON (tax_class.code_id = a.sqd_tax_class) LEFT OUTER JOIN loc_mstr f ON (f.loc_id = a.sqd_loc_id) INNER JOIN public.en_mstr ON (b.sq_en_id = public.en_mstr.en_id) INNER JOIN public.tranaprvd_dok j ON (public.en_mstr.en_id = j.tranaprvd_en_id)
